  "detailed_description": "In ROTA gravity bends beneath your feet! Move blocks and twist gravity to solve puzzles. Collect all 50 gems and explore 8 vibrant worlds!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993830/extras/aa069c4692057d91de4adebb3a9b649b.avif?t=1764093426\" width=650 height=162 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rotate gravity as you walk over the edge! <br></li><li>Push, pull and rotate gravity-blocks to traverse the stage and solve puzzles. <br></li><li>Collect all 50 gems to unlock doors and explore 8 vibrant worlds! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993830/extras/94b6d779dbcd003cfa8f740cbf01befe.avif?t=1764093426\" width=650 height=162 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Listen to an original ambient soundtrack that will keep you relaxed while solving challenging puzzles. (: <br></li><li>Watch out for spikes! 0: </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993830/extras/6bd6b60f397c359f77b966444e5d27c4.avif?t=1764093426\" width=650 height=162 /></span><br><br>ROTA is Open Source on GitHub!",
  "about_the_game": "In ROTA gravity bends beneath your feet! Move blocks and twist gravity to solve puzzles. Collect all 50 gems and explore 8 vibrant worlds!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993830/extras/aa069c4692057d91de4adebb3a9b649b.avif?t=1764093426\" width=650 height=162 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rotate gravity as you walk over the edge! <br></li><li>Push, pull and rotate gravity-blocks to traverse the stage and solve puzzles. <br></li><li>Collect all 50 gems to unlock doors and explore 8 vibrant worlds! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993830/extras/94b6d779dbcd003cfa8f740cbf01befe.avif?t=1764093426\" width=650 height=162 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Listen to an original ambient soundtrack that will keep you relaxed while solving challenging puzzles. (: <br></li><li>Watch out for spikes! 0: </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1993830/extras/6bd6b60f397c359f77b966444e5d27c4.avif?t=1764093426\" width=650 height=162 /></span><br><br>ROTA is Open Source on GitHub!",
